data.description: Move-In-Ready. Fantastic Knoxville Location. This large two-story home with a fully finished basement has much to offer. The home has been kept in impeccable condition showcasing approximately 3,750 square feet of living space spread across three levels, four bedrooms (with the potential for a fifth), three and a half bathrooms, a dining room, a living room/office, two cozy fireplaces, a beautiful kitchen, a bright breakfast room, a spacious great room, and a convenient main-level laundry room. Enjoy your morning coffee on the large screened porch.The second floor features four bedrooms, including a spacious master bedroom, and two full bathrooms. The lower level serves as extended living quarters with a recreation room featuring a fireplace, a full bathroom, and an office with a closet that can easily serve as a fifth bedroom if desired.Bamboo hardwood flooring adorns most of the main level and bedrooms all have walk in closets. Outside, you'll find a deck and LARGE private fenced backyard. There are too many incredible features to list with this home. Book your private showing today.
